text: My weekly craving for their herbal roast duck and their roast pork! Prices are so reasonable and food qualities are superb! They even offer free soup! üòçüòçüòç
A great bunch of young men working together to serve customers.
A delicious plate of duck rice. Duck has a bit of the herbal under taste and char Siew is roasted with a slightly sweet flavour; love the thick gravy over the rice too.

21/08/22
Had wonton noodle. The char siew is nice with sweet caramel flavour. The noodle is springy typical HK style. Overall not bad.

5 ‚≠ê The best Hainanese chicken rice, siew yoke, charsiew, wanton soup this part of Singapore. Chicken rice is great, wanton noodles are bouncy.

Fast and friendly service. Quick and efficient.

Super consistent food quality. Never failed for years!

I hope they remain in business for a long time!

I keep forgetting to take food pics. I start eating too fast!!
